time = calcTimeOfLastImpactOnPlane(
                self.startPos[2], endZ, self.startVel[2], self.zAcc)
            if time is None:
                self.notify.error(
                    'projectile never reaches plane Z=%s' % endZ)
            self.duration = time
            self.endPos = None

            self.notify.error('invalid set of inputs to ProjectileInterval')
